    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《桌面方块》是一个融合了消除和放置玩法的轻松桌面游戏，适合在忙碌中放松片刻。你可以在桌面的一角进行消除方块的挑战，随着消除的方块越多，分数也会不断提高。如果你没时间随时操作，游戏的放置系统会让它在后台持续生成资源，让你轻松积累。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>桌面环境</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《桌面方块》是一款<strong>小巧</strong>的游戏，专为在桌面的角落运行设计，因此不会占用太多空间。你可以一边使用电脑一边在角落体验游戏的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/766d2ccfe2380fbf28d519b22c46ed56.poster.avif?t=1731163553\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/766d2ccfe2380fbf28d519b22c46ed56.webm?t=1731163553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/766d2ccfe2380fbf28d519b22c46ed56.mp4?t=1731163553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>放置系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏会随时间自动生成点点资源，即使不操作，你也能持续获得资源。使用这些资源，你可以升级资源产出效率、增加库存容量，或购买新皮肤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/03122ca746a49cd5146df4351291c862.poster.avif?t=1731163553\" width=316 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/03122ca746a49cd5146df4351291c862.webm?t=1731163553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/03122ca746a49cd5146df4351291c862.mp4?t=1731163553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的皮肤</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内有丰富多样的皮肤选择，包括<strong>复古Windows 98画画工具</strong>、<strong>波普艺术风格</strong>、<strong>8-bit像素风</strong>等，满足不同审美需求。每种皮肤不仅改变方块外观，还带来独特的视觉体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/15b388c600f9d580e9a63b5d1ffb8ac3.avif?t=1731163553\" width=318 height=318 /></span></p>",
